text: Hola! Congratulations on reaching 7 days smoke-free! That's a huge accomplishment. I'm here to support you. How are you feeling today? Your stress level is at 5, is there anything specific causing you stress that I can help

- You're doing great, and it's normal to have fluctuations in stress levels. Keep in mind that your body is still adjusting to the absence of nicotine, and it's okay to feel a bit off sometimes. Stay hydrated, get enough sleep,
